window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I’m one of four Willow daughters. </p> <p>He’s the first-born son of the Scafoni family. And we have history.</p> <p>For generations, the Scafoni family have demanded a sacrifice of us. A virgin daughter to atone for sins so old, we don’t even remember what they are anymore.</p> <p>But when you have as much money as they do, you don’t play by the rules. You make them. </p> <p>And Sebastian Scafoni makes all the rules. </p> <p>The moment I saw him, I knew he would choose me. Even though the mark on my sheath declared me unclean. Even though my beautiful sisters stood beside me, offered to him, he still chose me. </p> <p>He made me his.</p> <p>And then he set out to break me. </p> <p><b>This set contains </b><b><i>Taken</i></b><b>,</b><b><i> Torn</i></b><b>, and</b><b><i> Twisted</i></b><b>, the complete Dark Legacy Trilogy.</b></p>"; 
